how i live now is a 2013 canadian-british speculative drama film based on the 2004 novel of the same name by meg &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it was directed by kevin macdonald and script written by tony grisoni , jeremy brock and penelope skinner . the film stars saoirse ronan , tom holland , anna chancellor , george mackay and corey johnson . it was screened in the special presentation section at the 2013 toronto international film festival .